24/7 咁查緊你d相， <br />\n樓主你無嫁喇，你一定比我地捉到你post露暈相.我地隨時接受你挑戰，你有種就post多d曝露。"},{"pid":"badabd649db449fcc8e6d17cb5ebdc7ef8997de0","tid":897734,"uid":59777,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:12:59.000Z","msg":"你覺得雞排會貼得出呢張相但係冇p走粒lin？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4544c5abd854291120dd09f2cc86b4eebc6b3984","tid":897734,"uid":3508,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"badabd649db449fcc8e6d17cb5ebdc7ef8997de0","tid":897734,"uid":59777,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:12:59.000Z","msg":"你覺得雞排會貼得出呢張相但係冇p走粒lin？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"貼左乳貼架<br />\n同埋出寫真都唔p圖執乾淨眼耳口鼻?當人傻的嗎?"},{"pid":"df6141c185ab2ae4d963c7bbb8f08f89cb1521e0","tid":897734,"uid":59777,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"4544c5abd854291120dd09f2cc86b4eebc6b3984","tid":897734,"uid":3508,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"badabd649db449fcc8e6d17cb5ebdc7ef8997de0","tid":897734,"uid":59777,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:12:59.000Z","msg":"你覺得雞排會貼得出呢張相但係冇p走粒lin？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo